    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To SortoutCode! ‚ù§Ô∏è To rotate the icons in BootstrapVue.We are going to use the  component of BootstrapVue.To rotate the icon by a‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To SortoutCode! ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>\n<p>To rotate the icons in BootstrapVue.We are going to use the <code class=\"language-text\">IconsPlugin</code> component of BootstrapVue.To rotate the icon by a specified number of degrees, we are going to use the <code class=\"language-text\">rotate</code> prop. The positive value will rotate icons clockwise and the negative value with rotate icons anticlockwise. </p>\n<p>Today I am going to show you <strong><em>How you rotate the icons in Bootstrap VueJS?</em></strong></p>\n<p>Table of contains</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Setup the Vue.js</li>\n<li>Install the Bootstrap and BootstrapVue</li>\n<li>Create FirstComponent.vue and import it into App.js</li>\n<li>Rotate the icons</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start today‚Äôs tutorial <strong><em>How do I rotate the icons in Bootstrap VueJS?</em></strong></p>\n<h2>Setup the Vue.js</h2>\n<p>First, we have to install the Vue project, I had installed the vueJS in my system. If you haven‚Äôt installed or have any problem with installation you can follow this article, which will show you step by step process of installation.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/blog/how-to-setup-vuejs-project/\" target=\"_BLANK\">How to Install the VueJS project?</a></p>\n<h2>Install the Bootstrap and BootstrapVue</h2>\n<p>First, we have to install the Vue project, I had installed the vueJS in my system. If you haven‚Äôt installed or have any problem with installation you can follow this article, which will show you step by step process of installation. In that article, I had also show you how to install BootstrapVue in your vue.js project step by step.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/blog/how-to-install-vue-bootstrap-in-vuejs/\" target=\"_BLANK\">How to install or configure vue-bootstrap in VueJS?</a></p>\n<h2>Create FirstComponent.vue and import it into App.js</h2>\n<p>Create the new component in the <code class=\"language-text\">src/components/</code> components folder. the component name is <code class=\"language-text\">FirstComponent.vue</code> and imported into the <code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code> file:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>template<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"app\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FirstComponent <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>template<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FirstComponent <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./components/FirstComponent.vue\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"App\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">components</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    FirstComponent<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>rotate the icons</h2>\n<p>After the install complete we have to register the <code class=\"language-text\">IconsPlugin</code> component in <code class=\"language-text\">src/main.js</code>.</p>\n<p>Bootstrap Icons are designed to work with Bootstrap components, from form controls to navigation. Bootstrap Icons are SVGs, so they scale quickly and easily and can be styled with CSS. While they are built for Bootstrap, they will work in any project.</p>\n<p>To rotate the icon by a specified number of degrees, we are going to use the <code class=\"language-text\">rotate</code> prop. The positive value will rotate icons clockwise and the negative value with rotate icons anticlockwise. Let‚Äôs see the code example:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">FirstComponent.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>template<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"font-size: 4rem;\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>Welcome to sortoutcode<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>icon icon<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar-chart\"</span> rotate<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"45\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>icon<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>icon icon<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar-chart\"</span> rotate<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"-45\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>icon<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>icon icon<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar-chart\"</span> rotate<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"180\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>icon<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>icon icon<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar-chart\"</span> rotate<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"-90\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>icon<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>template<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"FirstComponent\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>let‚Äôs check the output.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5acf04f6641a6f0e07fa7b7ef574f91f/cb425/rotate-the-icons-in-bootstrap-vuejs.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.835443037974684%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Add Icons\"\n        title=\"Add Icons\"\n        src=\"/static/5acf04f6641a6f0e07fa7b7ef574f91f/f058b/rotate-the-icons-in-bootstrap-vuejs.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5acf04f6641a6f0e07fa7b7ef574f91f/c26ae/rotate-the-icons-in-bootstrap-vuejs.png 158w,\n/static/5acf04f6641a6f0e07fa7b7ef574f91f/6bdcf/rotate-the-icons-in-bootstrap-vuejs.png 315w,\n/static/5acf04f6641a6f0e07fa7b7ef574f91f/f058b/rotate-the-icons-in-bootstrap-vuejs.png 630w,\n/static/5acf04f6641a6f0e07fa7b7ef574f91f/40601/rotate-the-icons-in-bootstrap-vuejs.png 945w,\n/static/5acf04f6641a6f0e07fa7b7ef574f91f/78612/rotate-the-icons-in-bootstrap-vuejs.png 1260w,\n/static/5acf04f6641a6f0e07fa7b7ef